    <briefdescription>
<para>A generic event <ref refid="classhelios_1_1event_1_1Dispatcher" kindref="compound">Dispatcher</ref> for type-safe event handling. </para>
    </briefdescription>
    <detaileddescription>
<para>The `Dispatcher` allows interested entities to subscribe to specific event types and dispatch events in a decoupled manner. Using `std::type_index` makes sure that only relevant handlers receive specific event instances. </para>
